01:16:51.440 --> 01:16:53.015
Yeah, he has flesh.

01:16:53.015 --> 01:16:54.480
We all have flesh.

01:16:55.520 --> 01:16:59.520
But the Lord said to keep the main thing the main thing and always go vertical.

01:16:59.520 --> 01:17:02.086
Keep your eyes on Him.

01:17:09.217 --> 01:17:09.514
And what does that entail for the church?

01:17:12.646 --> 01:17:19.440
To keep ourselves on our knees that we pray for him.

01:17:19.440 --> 01:17:20.525
We don't idolize or worship.

01:17:20.525 --> 01:17:21.480
'Oh, Trump's the greatest!

01:17:21.480 --> 01:17:22.280
Trump, Trump, Trump!

01:17:22.280 --> 01:17:25.420
' No, Jesus is the greatest.

01:17:35.320 --> 01:17:35.747
Jesus, Jesus, Jesus.

01:17:37.027 --> 01:17:46.871
And we thank you, Lord, that we have a man after your own heart that will lead this nation—one nation under God.

01:17:46.871 --> 01:17:49.480
Under God, not under Trump.

01:17:49.480 --> 01:17:50.560
Under God.

01:17:50.560 --> 01:17:52.267
'Well, Brandon, that's obvious.

01:17:52.267 --> 01:17:57.000
' No, it's not obvious to a lot of you.

01:17:57.000 --> 01:17:58.825
We get the emails.

01:17:58.825 --> 01:18:05.520
Regardless of Sister Clipboard out there going, 'Man, you're not talking to me.

01:18:05.520 --> 01:18:08.973
' Well, maybe not, keyboard warrior.

01:18:15.840 --> 01:18:16.108
I may not be talking to you, or maybe I am.

01:18:16.108 --> 01:18:28.120
But you need to get off your high horse and think about what I'm saying instead of typing away on your keyboard, always judging me.

01:18:29.080 --> 01:18:41.725
I'm trying to tell you, get on your face before a holy God and seek Him, and He will direct this path.

01:18:41.725 --> 01:18:43.000
He will direct Trump.

01:18:43.000 --> 01:18:47.074
He will do all that we need to do in the spirit realm.

01:18:47.074 --> 01:18:56.867
If we seek Jesus—'If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways'—then who will heal our land?

01:18:56.867 --> 01:18:57.382
Jesus.

01:18:57.382 --> 01:18:58.851
He will fix it.

01:18:58.851 --> 01:19:03.760
He's the one that's going to fix all this.

01:19:03.760 --> 01:19:06.880
Will he use Trump to do it?

01:19:15.810 --> 01:19:16.005
If that's what he wants to do.

01:19:16.005 --> 01:19:16.200
He could use you.

01:19:16.200 --> 01:19:18.144
Doesn't mean he has to use Trump.

01:19:18.144 --> 01:19:23.190
He can use whoever says, 'I am here, Lord, use me.

01:19:23.190 --> 01:19:23.760
Send me.

01:19:23.760 --> 01:19:26.510
' Some plant, some water, but God always brings forth the increase.

01:19:26.510 --> 01:19:30.227
It's not you who brings it, and neither is it Trump.

01:19:30.227 --> 01:19:31.047
It's Jesus.

01:19:31.047 --> 01:19:35.387
He will bring forth the increase in these end times.

01:19:35.387 --> 01:19:36.400
Jesus will.

01:19:36.400 --> 01:19:39.480
He will bring forth the repentance.

01:19:39.480 --> 01:19:42.080
He will do this.

01:19:42.080 --> 01:19:47.640
But it's through the church praying and not exalting a man.

01:19:47.640 --> 01:19:49.818
He is not Caesar Augustus.

01:19:49.818 --> 01:19:51.417
He is not whatever.

01:19:51.417 --> 01:20:00.440
We always need to give Jesus all the praise, and He will change the heart of Pharaohs.

01:20:00.440 --> 01:20:06.500
He has the heart of the king; the Bible says the heart of the king is in the hand of the Lord.

01:20:06.500 --> 01:20:09.033
So we pray for Donald Trump.

01:20:09.033 --> 01:20:11.920
We lift up his family.

01:20:11.920 --> 01:20:14.263
We lift up his marriage.

01:20:14.263 --> 01:20:16.320
The Lord said specifically pray over his marriage.

01:20:29.733 --> 01:20:29.880
The Lord said specifically pray for the safety of his kids and his grandkids.

01:20:40.897 --> 01:20:41.246
That's our job.

01:20:41.246 --> 01:20:50.343
Would I love to meet him one day and give him a hug and say, 'Great job, you're a good guy, man'?

01:20:50.343 --> 01:20:52.627
Just give you a hug.

01:20:52.627 --> 01:20:55.120
Do I agree with everything that you've done?

01:20:55.120 --> 01:20:55.611
No.

01:20:57.180 --> 01:21:01.349
But it's a lot better than Bush, it's a lot better than Obama, and it's certainly better than the Clintons.

01:21:03.120 --> 01:21:06.467
So we just go, "Hey God, this is who we have in there.

01:21:06.753 --> 01:21:12.720
" We pray for him to get across the finish line, but he is not a deity.

01:21:12.720 --> 01:21:13.840
Kim prophesied, Brandon.

01:21:13.840 --> 01:21:15.994
That's how many times Kim prophesied.

01:21:15.994 --> 01:21:18.320
I'm not rebutting what Kim Clement prophesied.

01:21:18.320 --> 01:21:19.476
I love Kim Clement.

01:21:19.476 --> 01:21:20.873
I love his family.

01:21:20.873 --> 01:21:23.440
I'm not rebutting that.

01:21:23.440 --> 01:21:32.086
I'm trying to tell you that regardless of what Kim Clement prophesied, it won't happen unless you pray him through it.

01:21:32.086 --> 01:21:33.400
Prophecy is free will.

01:21:50.229 --> 01:21:50.543
You can prophesy over me all day long and say, "Brandon, you're going to do this and you're going to do that.

01:21:50.543 --> 01:21:54.670
" But it's my free will to do it.

01:21:54.670 --> 01:22:01.190
Prophecies don't force you to do something; you still have free will.

01:22:03.040 --> 01:22:04.265
And it's still our job as a church to pray for him.

01:22:04.265 --> 01:22:06.600
Regardless of Kim Clement, R.

01:22:06.600 --> 01:22:07.080
W.

01:22:07.080 --> 01:22:09.354
Schambach, or whoever prophesied, I don't care.

01:22:09.354 --> 01:22:12.200
As I said, we all can miss it.

01:22:12.200 --> 01:22:16.940
As much as I love Kim Clement, I'm sure he can miss it.

01:22:19.097 --> 01:22:22.785
And if he was here today, he'd probably tell you the same thing: "Hey, I missed it before.

01:22:22.785 --> 01:22:24.750
" Have I missed it before?

01:22:24.750 --> 01:22:25.725
Is he a deity?

01:22:25.725 --> 01:22:26.265
No.

01:22:26.265 --> 01:22:29.093
He's a man just like Brandon Biggs.

01:22:29.093 --> 01:22:31.470
He's a man just like anybody else.

01:22:31.470 --> 01:22:33.164
Can Kim Clement miss it?

01:22:33.164 --> 01:22:34.120
I'm sure he could.

01:22:39.920 --> 01:22:40.540
Do I know that he has?

01:22:40.540 --> 01:22:41.440
I don't.

01:22:41.440 --> 01:22:59.600
I told his daughter, "I believe he's one of the most accurate prophets of this generation.

01:23:13.790 --> 01:23:14.020
" And I still stand by that.

01:23:14.020 --> 01:23:20.800
Now, do we always try to make his words fit when we think they should fit?

01:23:20.800 --> 01:23:24.160
Yeah, people do.

01:23:24.160 --> 01:23:31.560
He's not here to defend himself; the Lord took him home.

01:23:31.560 --> 01:23:33.045
He's gone.

01:23:33.045 --> 01:23:43.120
But where one general goes home, God raises up a new one and says, "Finish the race.

01:23:55.164 --> 01:23:55.387
" And if that general goes home, God will raise up another one and say, "Finish the race.

01:23:55.387 --> 01:23:55.831
Run.

01:23:55.831 --> 01:23:58.373
" It doesn't mean the job's done.

01:23:58.373 --> 01:24:05.394
When a major soldier dies on the battlefield, God brings up another soldier to grab the gun and keep going.

01:24:09.960 --> 01:24:10.150
And that's what we're seeing with this generation.

01:24:10.150 --> 01:24:11.480
He went home in 2015.

01:24:11.480 --> 01:24:13.284
God's raising up new voices.

01:24:13.542 --> 01:24:16.903
And that's what happens; it's called the cycle of life.

01:24:17.349 --> 01:24:19.131
So, we don't idolize people.

01:24:25.300 --> 01:24:25.520
The moment you start idolizing people instead of the Lord Jesus Christ, you're on the wrong road.

01:24:25.520 --> 01:24:29.527
I have to correct that a little bit tonight.

01:24:29.527 --> 01:24:35.966
There are so many of you who are on the wrong road.

01:24:35.966 --> 01:24:37.280
Look to Jesus.

01:24:37.280 --> 01:24:38.680
Stop idolizing prophetic voices.

01:24:38.680 --> 01:24:42.670
Stop idolizing ministers, presidents, and celebrities because man will let you down.

01:24:42.670 --> 01:24:44.840
Jesus will never let you down.

01:24:44.840 --> 01:24:55.357
Man will fail you; Jesus will never fail you.

01:24:55.357 --> 01:25:02.900
He's perfect and he loves you and he gave his life for you.

01:25:03.520 --> 01:25:07.320
And the moment we keep the main thing, we'll always be victorious.

01:25:07.320 --> 01:25:10.840
But if we get off and start getting weird, guess what?

01:25:10.840 --> 01:25:11.711
Correction will come.

01:25:11.711 --> 01:25:22.133
We have to keep our eyes on Jesus in these last days because many will see all these weird doctrines, doctrines of demons.

01:25:22.133 --> 01:25:50.720
Men will be swayed by doctrines of demons, and the Bible warned us it was coming.

01:25:50.720 --> 01:25:53.800
Many false prophets will rise.

01:25:53.800 --> 01:26:16.500
Don't allow yourself to be snared by false prophetic words and false teachings just because you see something.

01:26:17.570 --> 01:26:25.058
I told you they're going to perform miracles in the days ahead.

01:26:25.058 --> 01:26:28.480
They're going to raise the dead in the days ahead.

01:26:28.480 --> 01:27:36.048
And just because you see them perform a miracle and see signs and wonders in their ministry doesn't mean they're of God.

01:27:36.048 --> 01:27:41.970
You're going to have to know and have great discernment.

01:27:41.970 --> 01:27:57.488
Just because they walk in the supernatural...

01:27:57.488 --> 01:28:27.211
think about this: Pharaoh's men doing miracles and demonic stuff with their staffs and the snakes.

01:28:27.211 --> 01:29:29.929
They threw them down and Moses's snake ate theirs, but it didn't mean they couldn't perform the same kind of stuff, black magic, and the things they were doing.

01:29:29.929 --> 01:29:39.471
So be careful who you follow.

01:29:39.471 --> 01:29:43.480
Just because you see them do something, discern it.

01:29:43.480 --> 01:29:51.400
Be vigilant to filter in these last days because we're going to be snared if you don't.

01:30:06.933 --> 01:30:07.260
I don't care what they say.

01:30:07.260 --> 01:30:11.102
I don't care what they do.

01:30:11.102 --> 01:30:14.535
Always stay vertical and keep your eyes on Jesus.

01:30:14.535 --> 01:30:27.387
Keep him the main thing in these last days.

01:30:27.387 --> 01:30:30.590
If you don't, you're in trouble.

01:30:30.590 --> 01:30:35.422
We must keep Jesus first.

01:30:35.422 --> 01:30:51.310
And the Bible—back it up with the word.

01:30:51.320 --> 01:30:53.331
Read the word.

01:30:53.331 --> 01:30:57.103
Read it and read it some more.

01:31:24.891 --> 01:31:25.389
And the more you read it, the more you're going to know.

01:31:26.880 --> 01:31:38.778
The Bible says you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

01:31:38.778 --> 01:31:46.360
So we can't be following prophetic so-and-so all the time and saying, "That's it right there.

01:31:46.360 --> 01:31:49.240
That's set in stone.

01:31:49.240 --> 01:31:52.162
" Find it.

01:31:52.162 --> 01:32:06.007
Read the word.

01:32:06.007 --> 01:32:13.571
Keep your eyes on him.

01:32:13.571 --> 01:32:24.230
If it witnesses with you in your spirit that we're in the last days, then fine, keep running with it.

01:32:24.230 --> 01:32:25.105
If not, judge it.

01:32:25.105 --> 01:32:30.180
Keep quiet and just be still.

01:32:30.180 --> 01:32:38.177
Don't be so quick to jump on AI and all these things that we're about to see—many things to snare us.

01:32:38.177 --> 01:32:42.600
I hope that helps you because I feel like there's so much idolizing and weirdness.

01:32:42.600 --> 01:32:45.651
"Erica said this, she has the blue eyes, she's Esther.

01:32:45.651 --> 01:32:51.680
" I don't know if she's Esther; the Lord didn't give me that word.

01:32:51.680 --> 01:32:54.510
You can't ask him because he went home.

01:32:54.510 --> 01:33:04.086
All we know is we have a recording of him saying something.

01:33:17.865 --> 01:33:18.080
You have to just weigh things out and pray about it.

01:33:18.080 --> 01:33:21.982
It's healthy to really test the spirits, to sit there and listen.

01:33:21.982 --> 01:33:29.440
I didn't say be a sister with your clipboard and be mean; I said test in your own spirit and see if it witnesses with you.

01:33:29.440 --> 01:33:31.920
Is the Holy Spirit speaking this to me?

01:33:31.920 --> 01:33:35.760
Because I hear him just like that man can.

01:33:36.400 --> 01:33:48.500
I may not walk in the gifting of a prophet or a watcher, but I know that He said, "My sheep will know my voice and a stranger's voice I will not follow.

01:33:55.232 --> 01:33:55.848
" And those who are led by the spirit of God are the sons and the daughters of God.

01:34:02.320 --> 01:34:03.627
He didn't say be led by prophets; be led by the spirit of God in these last days.

01:34:11.517 --> 01:34:12.070
You must keep the main thing the main thing: Jesus.

01:34:12.080 --> 01:34:12.560
Vertical.

01:34:12.560 --> 01:34:16.142
I'm looking at you.

01:34:16.142 --> 01:34:18.629
Not all this stuff down here.

01:34:18.629 --> 01:34:20.480
There's too much static, too much noise.

01:34:20.480 --> 01:34:23.744
I'm keeping my eyes on you.

01:34:23.744 --> 01:34:25.280
Crack this Bible open.

01:34:25.280 --> 01:34:26.000
Read it.

01:34:26.884 --> 01:34:27.049
Take communion.

01:34:27.049 --> 01:34:28.200
Pray in the Holy Ghost.

01:34:28.200 --> 01:34:28.815
Sing songs.

01:34:28.815 --> 01:34:40.780
Whatever you have to do, but you've got to hear him for yourself.

01:34:42.760 --> 01:34:44.456
I'm telling you, I see a storm coming.

01:34:44.456 --> 01:35:09.425
Now, if that witnesses with you, fine.

01:35:09.425 --> 01:35:27.313
If you say, "Brandon, I feel like you missed it," well, I'm human.

01:35:39.229 --> 01:35:39.537
I pray I didn't.

01:35:39.537 --> 01:35:43.712
I'm doing the best I can.

01:35:43.712 --> 01:35:55.560
But please don't use anything that I say and go, "Hey, we're taking you by the word, Brandon.

01:35:55.560 --> 01:35:56.697
" That's foolish.

01:36:15.600 --> 01:36:21.700
Always judge the words even that I give and say, "Listen, I don't feel right.

01:36:21.700 --> 01:36:22.330
" Okay.

01:36:25.360 --> 01:36:26.520
I tell Sister Billye that all the time.

01:36:26.520 --> 01:36:28.777
If I'm wrong, rebuke me.

01:36:28.777 --> 01:36:34.017
Tell me I'm wrong, I'm false, and I need to get right.

01:36:39.160 --> 01:36:39.560
I am never above correction from my elders.

01:36:40.760 --> 01:36:49.531
I always tell them—from Billy Burke to Billye Brim to whoever—if you feel it's off, rebuke me and tell me.

01:36:55.920 --> 01:36:56.720
I am your elder, and I feel you're off and you need to be corrected.

01:36:59.200 --> 01:36:59.440
I listen.

01:36:59.440 --> 01:37:07.646
Give me a spiritual spanking through the Holy Ghost.

01:37:07.646 --> 01:37:22.600
I'm not above correction, but I am against the keyboard warriors in the comment section thinking they have spiritual stuff when you don't even know the difference between the Holy Ghost or whatever.

01:37:22.600 --> 01:37:35.128
I'm talking about people who are mature in the word of God, not people who have just been born again for two weeks and think they can correct you.

01:37:35.128 --> 01:37:36.056
No, no, no.

01:37:36.056 --> 01:37:42.976
I'll listen to the elders, but I'm not listening to such a keyboard warrior on there.

01:37:46.725 --> 01:37:47.350
Be still.

01:37:47.350 --> 01:39:06.813
You wouldn't know the Holy Ghost if he walked in and had HG on his head on a hat, Holy Ghost choir and angels behind you, and you're going, 'I wonder if that's the Lord.

01:39:06.813 --> 01:39:12.520
' I'm like, 'Yes, it's the Lord.

01:39:12.520 --> 01:39:14.240
' Just saying.

01:39:14.240 --> 01:39:39.771
Not trying to be rude, but there's a lot of you that are very immature.

01:39:39.771 --> 01:40:08.820
So, I say that all in love and I try to help as much as I can.

01:41:04.829 --> 01:41:05.723
And if you love me, you love me.

01:41:05.723 --> 01:41:10.153
If you don't, you don't.

01:41:10.153 --> 01:41:24.680
Lord said, 'Man, there's going to be a lot of people that hate you.

01:41:24.680 --> 01:41:32.400
' And I said, 'Well, okay, that's right.

01:41:59.240 --> 01:42:07.840
I stand with you and we do the best we can with what we give him, Lord.

01:42:07.840 --> 01:42:13.434
We seek you and we will find you.

01:42:13.434 --> 01:42:27.790
' And my job is always to point you to Jesus.

01:42:55.224 --> 01:42:55.808
You must know him.

01:42:55.808 --> 01:43:00.120
You must have a relationship with him.

01:43:00.120 --> 01:43:02.331
You're running out of time.

01:43:06.600 --> 01:43:23.432
I truly believe as we see the signs of the times all around us, you must know him.

01:43:23.432 --> 01:43:34.400
You must have a revelation of who he is.

01:43:34.400 --> 01:43:36.370
My sheep.

01:43:36.370 --> 01:43:38.107
Are you his?

01:43:38.107 --> 01:43:43.910
Do you belong to him?

01:43:43.920 --> 01:43:54.060
There's many of you tonight that sit here and say, 'Brandon, I don't know him.

01:43:54.060 --> 01:44:01.080
If I die tonight, where would I spend eternity?

01:44:01.080 --> 01:44:12.476
' Unless a man is born again, he will not enter into the kingdom of God.

01:44:12.476 --> 01:44:15.470
That's what my Bible says.

01:44:17.590 --> 01:44:20.130
So, you must know Jesus Christ.

01:44:20.130 --> 01:44:29.093
I'm going to ask you just real quick, do you know my friend?

01:44:29.093 --> 01:44:39.474
Before we go on, and you may say, 'I don't know him.

01:44:39.474 --> 01:45:01.485
' But I want to pray for you because tonight might be your last opportunity as those eight children went home to be with the Lord.

01:45:01.485 --> 01:45:02.910
There's so many people.

01:45:02.910 --> 01:45:08.654
There's perilous times all around us.

01:45:08.654 --> 01:45:12.930
And none of us are promised tomorrow.

01:45:16.180 --> 01:45:29.370
The very shoes you put on today to go to work, the very shoes you put on, the undertaker might be taking off that evening.

01:45:32.258 --> 01:45:33.720
You need to know there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

01:45:33.720 --> 01:46:29.260
And you need to know that Jesus Christ is the only way to the Father.

01:46:29.260 --> 01:46:50.274
Muhammad won't get you there.

01:46:50.274 --> 01:47:06.383
Buddha won't get you there.

01:47:06.383 --> 01:47:19.737
No satanic principality is going to get you there.

01:47:19.737 --> 01:47:24.560
The only way to the Father is through the Lord Jesus Christ.

01:47:24.560 --> 01:47:44.411
And tonight you have an opportunity to accept him as your Lord and Savior.

01:47:44.411 --> 01:47:52.912
I want to pray for you and just say a simple prayer right now.

01:47:52.912 --> 01:48:09.394
And all you have to do is accept Jesus Christ right now and repent and turn from your sins and say, 'Jesus, I make you my Lord and personal Savior tonight.

01:48:09.394 --> 01:48:20.989
' If I'm talking to you and you're watching this right now and you say, 'Brandon, after the first half, you shook me a little bit.

01:49:12.240 --> 01:50:47.270
I know I'm not living right.

01:50:47.280 --> 01:51:09.853
I've been living in sin.

01:51:09.853 --> 01:52:59.318
I've been going to the clubs.

01:52:59.328 --> 01:53:16.470
I've been doing things that I know that I shouldn't be doing.

01:53:16.480 --> 01:53:19.400
But tonight, I want to make things right.

01:53:19.400 --> 01:53:20.800
Tonight, I'm coming home.

01:53:29.120 --> 01:53:29.540
Will you please pray for me?

01:53:29.540 --> 01:53:32.180
' I would love to.

01:53:32.180 --> 01:53:38.406
But you've got to get real with God.

01:54:55.760 --> 01:54:57.016
And God's got to get real with you.

01:55:09.523 --> 01:55:10.264
The moment you get real with God, God will become real to you.

01:55:10.264 --> 01:55:37.860
So, I'm going to say a simple prayer, but I want you to be bold in your decision tonight.

01:56:06.720 --> 01:56:16.870
And I want you to say in the comment section tonight, 'Tonight's my night.

01:56:16.880 --> 01:56:18.070
I want to be saved.

01:56:18.070 --> 01:56:28.820
Tonight's my night.

01:56:28.820 --> 01:56:40.760
I'm coming home.

01:56:40.760 --> 01:57:11.091
' You may have been a person who was radically on fire for Jesus at one point in time in your life, but over the course of time, you've leaked out.

01:57:11.091 --> 01:57:16.427
You're not as full.

01:57:16.427 --> 01:57:21.377
You're not excited about Christianity anymore.

01:57:46.417 --> 01:57:46.846
You went back to the vomit that you repented over in the first place and said, 'Lord, I don't want to be a part of this anymore.

